startup:
hostname RouterA
ip ssh enable
ip ssh timeout 999999
interface gigabitethernet 0/0
 description to WAN
 ip address 172.16.30.141 255.255.255.0
 ip nat inside overload
exit
interface gigabitethernet 0/1
 description to RouterB
 ip address 10.0.1.1 255.255.255.240
exit
interface gigabitethernet 0/2
 description to routerC
 ip address 10.0.2.1 255.255.255.252
exit
router ospf
 network 10.0.1.0/28 area 0
 network 10.0.2.0/30 area 0
 network 172.16.30.0/24 area 1
 area 0
 exit
 area 1
 exit
exit
exit
running:
hostname RouterA-changed
ip ssh enable
ip ssh timeout 999999
banner motd My change in the running config
interface gigabitethernet 0/0
 description to WAN
 ip address 172.16.30.141 255.255.255.0
 ip nat inside overload
exit
interface gigabitethernet 0/1
 description to RouterB
 ip address 10.0.1.1 255.255.255.240
exit
interface gigabitethernet 0/2
 description to routerC
 ip address 10.0.2.1 255.255.255.252
exit
router ospf
 network 10.0.1.0/28 area 0
 network 10.0.2.0/30 area 0
 network 172.16.30.0/24 area 1
 area 0
 exit
 area 1
 exit
exit
exit
